<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="chr.wilck;;60" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">WChr60</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίων Ἡρακλείδῃ τῷ 

    <lb n="2"/>ἡμετέρῳ <expan>χα<ex cert="high">ίρειν</ex></expan>. ἔπεμψά σοι 

    <lb n="3"/>ἄλλας δύο <num value="2"/> ἐπιστολάς, 

    <lb n="4"/>διὰ Νηδύμου μίαν <num value="1"/>, διὰ 

    <lb n="5"/>Κρονίου μαχαιροφόρου 

    <lb n="6"/>μίαν <num value="1"/>· λοιπὸν οὖν <subst><add place="inline">ἔλα-

    <lb n="7"/>βον</add><del rend="corrected">ελαβος</del></subst> παρὰ <expan>το<ex cert="high">ῦ</ex></expan> Ἄραβος τὴν 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐπιστολὴν καὶ ἀνέ-

    <lb n="9"/>γνων καὶ <subst><add place="inline">ἐλυπήθην</add><del rend="corrected">εληπηθην</del></subst>. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἀκολούθει δὲ Πτολλ-

    <lb n="11"/>αρίωνι <subst><add place="inline">πᾶσαν</add><del rend="corrected">παραν</del></subst> ὥραν· τά-

    <lb n="12"/>χα δύναταί σε εὔλυτ-

    <lb n="13"/>ον <choice><corr>ποιῆσαι</corr><sic>ποισαι</sic></choice>· <subst><add place="inline">λέγε</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>γε</del></subst> αὐτῷ· ἄ-

    <lb n="14"/>λλο ἐγώ, ἄλλο πάντες, 

    <lb n="15"/>ἐγὼ παιδάριν εἰμί. παρὰ 

    <lb n="16"/>τὰ φο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρτ</supplied>ία μου· οὐκ οἶδα 

    <lb n="17"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="2.23">τί μ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε ὁ</supplied> πάτρων <choice><corr>ποιήσει</corr><sic>ποι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σει</unclear></sic></choice></lem><rdg>τιν<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>τρων<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ο<gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></rdg></app>, 

    <lb n="18"/>πολλοὺς <choice><corr>δανειστὰς</corr><sic>δανιστας</sic></choice> ἔχο-

    <lb n="19"/>μεν. μὴ ἵνα ἀναστατώ-

    <lb n="20"/>σῃς ἡμᾶς, ἐρώτα αὐτὸ<add place="supralinear">ν</add> 

    <lb n="21"/>καθ᾽ ἡμέραν· τάχα δύνα-


    <lb n="22"/>ταί σε <subst><add place="inline">ἐλεῆσαι</add><del rend="corrected">εεεησαι</del></subst>· ἐὰν μή, ὡς 

    <lb n="23"/>ἂν πάντες καὶ σὺ βλέ-

    <lb n="24"/>πε <choice><corr>σεαυτὸν</corr><sic>σατον</sic></choice> ἀπὸ τῶν Ἰου-

    <lb n="25"/>δαίων. μᾶλλον ἀκολουθῶ<add place="supralinear">ν</add> 

    <lb n="26"/>αὐτῷ δύνῃ φιλιάσαι αὐτῷ· 

    <lb n="27"/>ἰδέ, <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>η</sic></choice> δύναται διὰ Διοδώρου 

    <lb n="28"/>ὑπογραφῆναι ἡ τάβλα διὰ 

    <lb n="29"/>τῆς γυναικὸς τοῦ <app type="BL"><lem resp="9.25">Ἡγεμ-

    <lb n="30"/>όνος</lem><rdg>ἡγεμόνο?</rdg></app> · ἐὰν τὰ <expan>παρ<ex cert="high">ὰ</ex></expan> <choice><corr>σεαυτοῦ</corr><sic>σατου</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ποιή-

    <lb n="31"/>σῃς</corr><sic>ποισης</sic></choice>, οὐκ εἶ μεμπτός. 

    <lb n="32"/>ἀσπάζου Διόδωρον <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.95"><expan>μεγάλω<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan></lem><rdg>μ<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>αλων</rdg></app>. 

    <lb n="33"/><expan>ἔρρω<ex cert="high">σο</ex></expan>. ἀσπάζου <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.95">Ἁρποχράτιον</lem><rdg>Ἁρποχράτη<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied></rdg></app>. 

    <lb n="34"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> Τιβερίου Κλαυδίου <expan>Καίσαρο<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="35"/><expan>Σεβα<ex cert="high">στοῦ</ex></expan> Γερμανικοῦ <expan>Αὐτοκρά<ex cert="high">τορος</ex></expan> <expan>μηνὸ<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="36"/>Καισαρείου <num value="11">ια</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀπόδος εἰς</supplied> <expan>Ἀλεξά<ex cert="high">νδρειαν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="2"/>εἰς <expan>Σεβα<ex cert="high">στὴν</ex></expan> <expan>Ἀγορὰ<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> ε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἰς</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὴν</supplied> <gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>θήκην ὥστε <expan>Ἡρακλ<ex cert="high">είδῃ</ex></expan> <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> <expan>Σαραπίω<ex cert="high">νος</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="4"/><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ωνος <expan>το<ex cert="high">ῦ</ex></expan> Σωσιπάτρου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="41" notBefore="41" type="textDate" value="0041-08-04">4. Aug. 41</date></p></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zum Ort vgl. BL VIII, S. 40.</p></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">BGU</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1079</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">9456</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0001</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1079</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0001;4;1079" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">40</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">25</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">W.Chr. 60</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Sel. Pap. I 107</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">C.Pap.Jud. II 152</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.9456" part="N" subtype="translat